display="inline"><![CDATA[H]]></fr:tex> is a Hodge structure of weight <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>, then we define a mixed Hodge structure with the same integral lattice and the same Hodge filtration by setting
    <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[       W_i(H_\mathbb {Q}) =       \begin {cases}         0 &\text {for } i<n     \\H_\mathbb {Q} &\text {for } i\geqslant  n.       \end {cases}     ]]></fr:tex></fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
